249
00:15:20.470 --> 00:15:22.840
Well.just...
stay away from me.

250
00:15:23.350 --> 00:15:25.110
Fair warning.

251
00:15:32.780 --> 00:15:34.500
Ew.hair.

252
00:15:35.800 --> 00:15:37.010
Yeah.

253
00:15:39.940 --> 00:15:41.090
What are you doing?

254
