262
00:16:18.550 --> 00:16:23.660
I just got a fax confirming that the 
city of has unanimously voted you

263
00:16:24.080 --> 00:16:25.980
santa barbara exorcist of the year.

264
00:16:26.720 --> 00:16:28.580
Okay...
make all your little jokes.

265
00:16:28.580 --> 00:16:30.910
but I know who was right on my 
ass all the way to the car.

266
00:16:30.910 --> 00:16:32.390
I had no choice.
You were my ride home.

267
00:16:32.390 --> 00:16:33.500
Shawn.you were screaming.too.

268
00:16:33.500 --> 00:16:37.400
Yes.I was screaming."gus.stop! 
Let's be brave!¡±

269
