non sensical gibberish.

285
00:17:19.760 --> 00:17:22.360
XXXXXXXXXXX

286
00:17:23.420 --> 00:17:26.960
Acnaib...

287
00:17:29.560 --> 00:17:30.840
acnaib...

288
00:17:30.840 --> 00:17:33.020
acnaib.
I don't know.

