and who's going to fuse the planter's punch?

299
00:18:12.880 --> 00:18:15.380
Oh.yeah.and by the way.met alice bundy today.

300
00:18:15.380 --> 00:18:17.180
Not a shiny happy person.

301
00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:18.340
- I think maybe--
- jules!

302
00:18:18.340 --> 00:18:19.880
Doreen didn't kill herself!

303
00:18:19.880 --> 00:18:23.730
She was not alone in that room.
and we need to talk to bianca right now!

304
