and we're supposed 
to lead the slow clap.

309
00:18:42.070 --> 00:18:44.350
Just go without me.
You don't have to wait.

310
00:18:44.820 --> 00:18:46.500
Okay.this is ridiculous.

311
00:18:46.500 --> 00:18:48.500
Just open the door.
I'm coming in there.

312
00:18:49.110 --> 00:18:51.330
