313
00:18:52.310 --> 00:18:56.040
Even if I wanted to.my fingers 
and toes are all pruney now.

314
00:18:56.620 --> 00:18:57.780
Ew.

315
00:19:06.010 --> 00:19:08.930
Bianca.open the door.
This is completely ridiculous.

316
00:19:12.840 --> 00:19:13.600
Hello?

317
00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:15.590
Mary lou.it's bianca!
Help!

318
00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:34.220
Jules?

319
00:19:42.320 --> 00:19:43.700
Betty.if you know something.

320
