335
00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:22.520
Yes.yes.it broke!

336
00:20:22.530 --> 00:20:23.730
That's it.Don't you see?

337
00:20:23.740 --> 00:20:25.220
We never meant for her to fall!

338
00:20:25.230 --> 00:20:26.590
It was a complete accident!

339
00:20:27.030 --> 00:20:28.130
Oh.my god.bianca!

340
00:20:28.140 --> 00:20:29.310
What the hell did you do?

341
