Okay.please.do continue.

342
00:20:33.440 --> 00:20:34.400
Okay.like.it was.

343
00:20:34.410 --> 00:20:36.400
it was my job to get doreen into the house.

344
00:20:36.820 --> 00:20:38.380
She knew that it was a haze.

345
00:20:38.390 --> 00:20:40.740
She thought that she was supposed
to spend the whole night inside.

346
00:20:41.150 --> 00:20:43.530
Like that movie with the hedge
