Hell night.

348
00:20:44.630 --> 00:20:45.700
Exactly.

349
00:20:45.710 --> 00:20:49.340
Bianca was inside.wearing
this nightgown.you know.like.

350
00:20:49.350 --> 00:20:51.510
like scary sherry.the
girl who jumped from--

351
00:20:51.520 --> 00:20:52.660
we know.

352
00:20:52.670 --> 00:20:53.520
Nightgown.

353
00:20:53.990 --> 00:20:56.200
nightgown.I'm feeling the nightgown.

354
00:20:57.900 --> 00:20:59.160
Put it in.

355
