Dude.you have to come.

388
00:22:32.780 --> 00:22:34.120
Ooh.I don't know about that.shawn.

389
00:22:34.130 --> 00:22:36.610
Seems like a pretty big deal.
him reaching out and all.

390
00:22:36.620 --> 00:22:37.950
