and if there is.we're going
to pretend like there isn'T.

402
00:23:00.240 --> 00:23:02.510
This girl is sharon stone
from basic instinct.

403
00:23:03.070 --> 00:23:04.500
which makes me michael douglas.

404
00:23:04.510 --> 00:23:06.010
and you george dzundza.

405
