whose name is actually gus in the film!

406
00:23:09.420 --> 00:23:11.420
Until we have another lead.
we assume it's her.

407
00:23:11.430 --> 00:23:13.420
We've just got to figure out the "how."

408
00:23:13.430 --> 00:23:15.380
So far.no ice pick.

409
00:23:15.390 --> 00:23:19.290
Okay.first of all.don't ever compare
my black ass to george dzundza again.okay?

410
00:23:19.690 --> 00:23:20.250
Fair.

411
00:23:20.260 --> 00:23:22.890
And what could you possibly ask that
girl that the police already haven't?

412
00:23:23.830 --> 00:23:25.150
Want to split a pineapple?

413
