I'm sorry.do I know you?

414
00:23:27.070 --> 00:23:28.520
My name is ichabod fletchman.

415
00:23:28.530 --> 00:23:31.020
"Sticky icky" to my boys.but
that's neither here nor there.

416
00:23:31.030 --> 00:23:34.630
What's important is that
this baby is 82% hawaiian.

417
00:23:34.920 --> 00:23:36.920
and I've got all afternoon.

418
00:23:36.930 --> 00:23:38.660
Are you a crazy person?

419
