to make toast" to the end of mine.

421
00:23:47.060 --> 00:23:48.250
Right.

422
00:23:48.260 --> 00:23:49.940
So you're another cop.then?

423
00:23:49.950 --> 00:23:50.920
Not a cop.

424
00:23:50.930 --> 00:23:51.950
Not even close.

425
00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:53.410
Well.then who are you?

426
