Oh.come on.

432
00:24:14.570 --> 00:24:16.160
I was trying to be cool.

433
00:24:16.520 --> 00:24:17.890
What do you want from me?

434
00:24:17.900 --> 00:24:20.290
You want to read my palm?

435
00:24:20.300 --> 00:24:21.570
Would you like a lock of my hair?

436
00:24:21.580 --> 00:24:23.460
Whoa.alice.

437
00:24:24.140 --> 00:24:25.330
Now.I can.

438
00:24:25.340 --> 00:24:27.290
I can feel that you're
hurting-- really?

439
00:24:27.300 --> 00:24:28.930
Can you feel that I'm hurting?

440
