Come on.psychic.you can do
better than that.can't you?

441
00:24:32.950 --> 00:24:34.370
Do you have a best friend?

442
00:24:34.380 --> 00:24:37.120
Yeah.Uh.since birth.almost.

443
00:24:37.130 --> 00:24:39.600
Great.so then maybe you could
wrap your head around this.

444
00:24:40.390 --> 00:24:42.570
Doreen and i were closer than sisters.

445
00:24:42.980 --> 00:24:44.770
Her parents took me in when I was seven.

446
00:24:45.570 --> 00:24:46.750
Seven.

447
00:24:46.760 --> 00:24:47.710
They raised me.

448
00:24:47.720 --> 00:24:49.260
We did everything together.

449
00:24:49.270 --> 00:24:51.220
and the one time that I wasn't there.

450
00:24:51.540 --> 00:24:55.020
the one time I let her down.
and now she's gone.

451
00:24:56.780 --> 00:24:58.800
I know if anything 
happened to gus.I would.uh.

452
00:24:59.970 --> 00:25:01.370
I don't know.I've never.

453
00:25:01.380 --> 00:25:02.850
I mean.I was.

454
