I mean.I understand your
suspicion and everything.

457
00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:14.160
but I'm barely hanging on here.

458
00:25:14.170 --> 00:25:16.230
and I just don't think that.

459
00:25:18.900 --> 00:25:20.710
