460
00:25:22.270 --> 00:25:24.460
Well.I certainly hope not for your sake.

461
00:25:26.460 --> 00:25:29.100
Someone came in and emptied the
cash register when I was in the back.

462
00:25:30.150 --> 00:25:31.630
You're not writing this down?

463
00:25:32.270 --> 00:25:33.980
Who's got the arthritic thumb here?

464
00:25:35.070 --> 00:25:37.900
I hitchhiked from jersey
to havana when I was 19.

465
00:25:39.000 --> 00:25:40.160
For crying out loud.

466
00:25:40.800 --> 00:25:43.230
they also got away with
about $60 worth of rump roast.

467
00:25:43.240 --> 00:25:47.250
Don't try to sell me on
that nonsense.you punk!

468
00:25:47.860 --> 00:25:50.300
What.do you think this is 
my first square dance?

469
00:25:55.650 --> 00:25:57.080
Give me your gun.lassiter.

470
00:25:57.410 --> 00:25:59.600
I'll show you how to make 
this little pig squeal.

471
00:26:02.040 --> 00:26:03.340
You're just going to let him go?

472
00:26:03.350 --> 00:26:04.860
He's the victim.goochberg!

473
00:26:04.870 --> 00:26:05.970
Fine!Fine!

474
00:26:05.980 --> 00:26:07.820
I'll do it myself!

475
00:26:11.480 --> 00:26:12.890
Mary lou.wait!

476
00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:18.560
I totally almost forgot to give this to you.

477
00:26:18.570 --> 00:26:19.740
Well.what is it.eden?

478
00:26:20.110 --> 00:26:21.350
I don't know.

479
00:26:21.360 --> 00:26:23.070
It was left on the stoop.like.

480
00:26:23.080 --> 00:26:25.240
like a little baby orphan.

481
00:26:28.130 --> 00:26:29.910
"God's gift is forgiveness."

482
00:26:29.920 --> 00:26:31.820
Please join us in remembering our daughter.

483
00:26:31.830 --> 00:26:34.340
