484
00:26:34.930 --> 00:26:36.060
Tonight?

485
00:26:36.070 --> 00:26:36.910
Hello!

486
00:26:36.920 --> 00:26:37.810
Plans.

487
00:26:38.520 --> 00:26:40.390
- Bye!
- Bye!

488
00:26:45.810 --> 00:26:47.700
